The paper deals with semantic segmentation, which is a computer vision task, hence cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques, which falls under cs.LG and cs.AI. The paper also mentions the use of weak annotations, which is a topic in natural language processing, hence cs.CL is a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with generating mask predictions, which is a topic in multimedia, hence cs.MM is also a possible sub-category.
